timing_disabl...ntention_check(25.10)    timing_disabl...ntention_check(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_bus_contention_check

Syntax
       timing_disable_bus_contention_check

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to  true,  disables propagation of maximum delay along three
       state disable timing arcs and minimum delay along  three  state  enable
       arcs.  If  you know that bus contention conditions do not occur in your
       design, disable these checks by setting these globals to true.

       Checks for setup and hold violations in three-state bus designs. Checks
       the worst delay path to ensure that the latched signals are stable  and
       not  unknown  values  -  X.  Ensures  proper timing checks for bus con-
       tention.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

